{"tid":300432,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"東京食壽司，因為一個港女同事既ON9行為俾人趕左出鋪","createTime":"2017-06-28T01:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T16:40:21.000Z","uid":28938,"like":4,"dislike":327,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72e885ad9cf809739e57be8f3281b0b8be42f777","tid":300432,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:43:59.000Z","msg":"今個星期幾個同事去東京開會，公事完畢，尋晚搵左間幾出名既壽司店醫肚<br />\n<br />\n點知其中一個女同事原來唔食生魚，事前問過佢又唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n師傅一路整壽司，我地一路食，味道真係好鮮！但個女同事唔食，淨係食左鰻魚壽司同玉子燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n師傅見佢唔對路，用英文問佢係唔係對味道有滿意<br />\n<br />\n點知個港女竟然問師傅可唔可以俾佢一個爐仔，焯熟d魚生黎食，話覺得生食魚生唔係幾衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n師傅聽到後面色一變，同知客講左幾句；個知客行埋黎請我地即刻走，錢都唔收 ，話我地唔尊重佢地既食物。<br />\n<br />\n依家等上機，個港女同事仲係堅持自己無錯，話佢地唔識serve客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db767c992143155d4517b79a8256948adea108d1","tid":300432,"uid":59690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03261fc7495538fc6e3dd94a3bf94c1f1269970","tid":300432,"uid":74302,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"你女同事支那人？"},{"pid":"32bd74b6a128b5f568a8af6caceafd211d173590","tid":300432,"uid":37733,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:55:50.000Z","msg":"唔食魚生食乜鬼野壽司"},{"pid":"7711dff30c789c14bd4bb2e7c13b78fad7be8ce5","tid":300432,"uid":107623,"like":19,"dislike":119,"score":-100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:58:11.000Z","msg":"其實你應該問下係咪個個人都食到生野先。<br />\n佢問人有無爐係鳩，但佢唔食係無錯。而且老闆唔過黎佢本來都唔會問，好明顯係就緊你地。"},{"pid":"638f21064301d5ef8778a666426f8e4f8d000f02","tid":300432